<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>WAITING FOR THE LORD'S COMING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nanghaw, Lalpa hungkitna ding ngaktehaw,
 A hungkitna ding chuh genviel un;
 Gamla takhaw a chun vakviel viel unla,
 &quot;Hungvak ding ei tai&quot; tin genviel un.

[V2]
 Nitiem chuh a naitai, A hung kitna ding,
 Ni chuh tawmin, hun a chawm tai;
 Tatsate'n la sau hen a hungkit muokna'n,
 Namtin kiguong zo un.

[V3]
 2. Nanghaw Lalpa hungna ding ngakte haw chun,
 Ipmu chuh phawng un, paucham sak un;
 Vana Moneipa chuh hungvak ding eitai,
 Entiem u, A hung kipan ei tai.

[V4]
 3. Zion Lalpa chungnung chawian zing hitiu,
 Thiemgaute'n le a na gen u chuh;
 Lasa'n chawian un, Lalpa chuh Angelte'n,
 Ama ah kipahna thu gen un.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>145</hymn_number>
</song>